issue.title: [CF 995] Log in error TMW global error
issue.body:
IMPORTANT: If your issue is only occurring with a specific icon, include an export string of the icon in this ticket. Subsequently, if the issue involves an entire group or an entire profile, include the entire export string of the group or profile.

comments.body:
You created a Lua snippet in TMW and gave it some invalid code. Go into TMW's main options and either disable the snippet, delete it, or fix it. It's called "new snippet".


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras

LOL thanks i totally forgot about that i added that snippet, thanks this did fix the error! I feel kinda stupid that i forgot about that , thanks alot.


> Posted by CurseForge user Mayotruck
